        <p>
          If you are a contractual developer or a representative of a person,
          please ask them to purchase the product from us directly. It saves
          time on both sides when we follow up on support tickets.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p><strong>3. Refund Policy</strong></p>
        <p>
          We are so confident that you will definitely LOVE and BENEFIT from our
          products; we offer a 15-day no-questions-asked refund policy.
        </p>
