          any notice. This may be due to one or several of the following
          reasons. Abusive behavior and/or excessive negativity towards the
          ZeptoApps staff. Repeated defamatory, malicious, and/or false
          statements, including slander against ZeptoApps. Promoting competitor
          products, contributing to software piracy, hacking, spamming, or other
          illegal acts. We reasonably believe that our client has been
          compromised, shared with others, or for other security reasons. All
          decisions are final, and terminated support will not be reversed.
        </p>
      </div>
